snippet: LEAD: The California Legislature, breaking a record 28-day deadlock, has sent Gov. George Deukmejian a $55 billion budget and 18 related bills on fees, taxes, savings, budget cutting and prisons....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: The California Legislature, breaking a record 28-day deadlock, has sent Gov. George Deukmejian a $55 billion budget and 18 related bills on fees, taxes, savings, budget cutting and prisons.

headline.main: Deadlock Is Broken on California's Budget
